{"tid":253551,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［減肥無極限］有冇巴絲試過埋線減肥？","createTime":"2017-05-22T13:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T22:19:36.000Z","uid":71051,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a60888072b00308de9f003274df6683217e79d","tid":253551,"uid":71051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"肥妹就係唔肯正正經經減肥<br />\n呢排睇到埋線減肥郁d就一個月瘦5kg<br />\n心郁郁<br />\n想問巴絲有冇試過邊間？<br />\nGoogle過澳門醫院做就$500內一次<br />\n香港好多選擇 但唔個邊間好<br />\n暫時book左醫纖美 第一次$699<br />\nIg睇有間好似好勁 叫xxsoslim<br />\n但天價黎 $4800一次<br />\n醫院做都唔洗呢個價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個間醫纖美唔肯講個中醫師叫咩名 覺得有d奇怪<br />\n但上網search唔到有關資料"},{"pid":"dfe89043ac770053948bfd7815d4d8246a82c6a8","tid":253551,"uid":71051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"6e9009a80b09a3208c2332f5bbd9d82e9450abdf","tid":253551,"uid":71051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"67b1d7b0ad2722fec419985d161c4101aa0b621e","tid":253551,"uid":91216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"我有朋友試左4800個果<br />\n10日5磅<br />\n但我都係覺得好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5c1a8617073f0ee16896b79ade4227f7ec744f","tid":253551,"uid":34556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:21:57.000Z","msg":"試過一次 好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話食慾會減低 但感覺唔到"},{"pid":"e751b750dbda9963031310b924ea416189661041","tid":253551,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過一次 好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話食慾會減低 但感覺唔到</blockquote><br />\n有冇減到？"},{"pid":"9840bb3d69810d2f1a6a9d0521147ba819f5c771","tid":253551,"uid